this four month probationary period, if shown to act or behave in ways detrimental to the Black Tower, will be unguilded by the guildmaster after a majority voting of all guild officers. A voting thread will be posted on the officer forum in which all officers have 1 week to enter their vote. This vote will be binding, and can only be overturned by the guildmaster.<br><br>~~~New guildmates can not sponsor potential recruits during their 4 month evaluation period.<br><br>~~~As a new member of the family you are required to have a profile of your character, posted under the profiles forum on the website, using the Magelo software. If you can not access a Magelo account, for whatever reason, it is your responsibility to post your current equipment so that an account can be setup by a fellow guildmate.<br><br>~~~All new recruits must have an ezboard account in order to access the Black Tower message board. If you can not create an account then you must contact another member of the Black Tower so they can assist you in setting one up. <br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub83.ezboard.com/fmalysblacktowerboardfrm29.showPrevMessage?topicID=3.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub83.ezboard.com/fmalysblacktowerboardfrm29.showNextMessage?topicID=3.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fmalysblacktowerboardfrm29.emailToFriend?topicID=3.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fmalysblacktowerboardfrm29.threadControl?topicID=3.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub83.